{"segment_id": "shijing__daya-dang-005__001__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "daya-dang-005", "source_id": "daya-dang-005__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "詩經·大雅·蕩之什·005.1", "text_original": "崧高維嶽，駿極于天。維嶽降神，生甫及申。\n維申及甫，維周之翰。四國于蕃，四方于宣。", "text_normalized": "崧高維嶽，駿極于天。維嶽降神，生甫及申。\n維申及甫，維周之翰。四國于蕃，四方于宣。", "notes": "崧高 Chinese stanza 1."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__daya-dang-005__002__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "daya-dang-005", "source_id": "daya-dang-005__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 2, "canonical_ref": "詩經·大雅·蕩之什·005.2", "text_original": "亹亹申伯，王纘之事。于邑于謝，南國是式。\n王命召伯，定申伯之宅。登是南邦，世執其功。", "text_normalized": "亹亹申伯，王纘之事。于邑于謝，南國是式。\n王命召伯，定申伯之宅。登是南邦，世執其功。", "notes": "崧高 Chinese stanza 2."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__daya-dang-005__003__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "daya-dang-005", "source_id": "daya-dang-005__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 3, "canonical_ref": "詩經·大雅·蕩之什·005.3", "text_original": "申伯之功，召伯是營。有俶其城，寢廟既成。\n既成藐藐，王錫申伯。四牡蹻蹻，鉤膺濯濯。", "text_normalized": "申伯之功，召伯是營。有俶其城，寢廟既成。\n既成藐藐，王錫申伯。四牡蹻蹻，鉤膺濯濯。", "notes": "崧高 Chinese stanza 3."}
